ail at high","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"zoom levels. The default value is 18.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing an integer; specifies the size of the tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer on each side. A value of 0 produces no buffer. A value of 512 produces a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer as wide as the tile itself. Larger values produce fewer rendering","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"artifacts near tile edges and slower performance. The default value is 128.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionbuffer","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text"